{"type": "article", "id": 26657, "title": "极简卷笔器", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-11T06:44:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016070212570592PquBJ1iwyNYDtI.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\">这款极简风格的<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/36820783/Zirconia-Sharpener\">卷笔器</a>由 <a href=\"http://www.bryanwongdesign.com/\">Bryan Wong</a> 和 <a href=\"http://www.chengtaoyi.com/\">Chengtao Yi</a> 共同设计，由一整块白色的锆石陶瓷制成。和其他卷笔器具最大的区别在于它利用锆石本身来切削铅笔，相比普通的卷笔刀在耐用程度上有了很大的提升。简洁的外形以及陶瓷的质感也是它的加分项，可惜的是目前还未开始出售。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125703Ku6QVqjLU3dPIAGt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125703ukQZLR8dHejaX21Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125704RIC9YrXTaWBNcSn5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021257045a10exdAJsjMWcH3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}